summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Roy C. Erickson and Marcella Erickson, his wife, William Wee and Ricka Wee, his wife, G. B. Johannson and Isabelle G. Johannson, his wife, to the City of Seattle, and laying off Parket Court, also laying off Parker Court over and across the lands adjoining, heretofore accepted by the City for alley purposes, under Ordinance No. 60132.
